subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Bryant Hahnfeldt kicked a 33-yard field goal with two seconds remaining Saturday to give Vanderbilt an upset victory over No. 16 Georgia, which lost to an unranked team for the first time since 2002.
